A '''scrub chamber''' was a method of personal sanitation used by the [[Yevetha]] onboard their [[Starship/Legends|ships]]. It started as a soft needle-spray shower of [[Water/Legends|water]], followed by a painful surge of scrub jets.

==Appearances==
*''[[Before the Storm]]''

